Stop sharing platform_dma_configure() helper as they are about to have
their own bus dma_configure callbacks.

Signed-off-by: Lu Baolu <baolu.lu@linux.intel.com>
Reviewed-by: Jason Gunthorpe <jgg@nvidia.com>
